{"tid":1687163,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"其實命有冇得改","createTime":"2019-11-01T15:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T07:40:42.000Z","uid":125976,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5feeaa90db600dc90feac7f9d3a2c05dd3c8466","tid":1687163,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"如果有得積陰德<br />\n點解有啲人做成世好事都好兜踎？<br />\n點解又有啲人愈仆街愈風光？<br />\n<br />\n有人話係前世今生又唔係好講得通<br />\n真係大把人大半世做好人都生活得好慘<br />\n唔通嗰啲人前世真係十惡不赦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話係上帝早已預備<br />\n佢整咗個又仆街又風光嘅<br />\n跟住又整多個又好人又兜踎嘅<br />\n咁上帝係咪真係透過拯救個又好人又兜踎嘅嚟榮耀自己？<br />\n又好似講唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你話人定勝天<br />\n又真係好多人付出十倍努力都係仆晒街<br />\n又有啲人行起狗屎運上嚟冇料都成功到<br />\n命運係咪真係機率嘅問題？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd208b5ffeb91257b059daf4a526908e47030a0","tid":1687163,"uid":34714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"6da7b09c39f8622604912387840eeb546eedb65e","tid":1687163,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:40:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14701fb0b9ee92320b09262a0e3bb10e271e6502","tid":1687163,"uid":125976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6da7b09c39f8622604912387840eeb546eedb65e","tid":1687163,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:40:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"殺人放火改姓党<br />\n修橋鋪路毀香港"},{"pid":"d4e3a0badd8998db0ee519c1cdd25f2fffbbad5b","tid":1687163,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"攞盆水照下。。。"},{"pid":"badf33d7b99fc9ce0b3dd7f0a9f3fc948d320e21","tid":1687163,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T18:43:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1a957b3eed6ed9c